Once a month we need to refresh our Slack [invite
link](http://inside.gratipay.com/appendices/chat). There's a recurring
[calendar](/appendices/calendar) item about it to hopefully remind us. Generate
a new &ldquo;[shared
invite](https://gratipay.slack.com/admin/shared_invites)&rdquo; link and update
it in
[`appendices/chat`](https://github.com/gratipay/inside.gratipay.com/blob/master/www/appendices/chat.spt).
